{"tid":404808,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港獨殺無赦？】曾樹和笠水cut記者線 牧師感不安報警冀阻歪風","createTime":"2017-09-18T11:30:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T12:07:24.000Z","uid":39464,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca0394f62850a50f19aa3dbe798a15484c4ce9f9","tid":404808,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T11:30:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170918/large/1505726601_1d48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170918%2Flarge%2F1505726601_1d48.jpg&h=28efdd75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曾樹和曾於台上大叫口號「搞港獨者必須要殺！」，並由何君堯附和高呼「無赦」。（黎樹雄攝）<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員何君堯昨在添馬公園舉行的「革走戴耀廷吶喊大會」，有份出席的屏山鄉鄉事委員會主席曾樹和曾大叫口號「搞港獨者必須要殺！」，並由何君堯附和高呼「無赦」。《蘋果》今天就事件聯絡曾樹和回應，而他未等及記者提出問題，即表示：「我唔發表&hellip;&hellip;我唔發表任何嘢，OK？」，隨即掛斷電話。<br />\n<br />\n今日下午有市民稱因對該番「港獨殺無赦」言論深感不安，而決定到灣仔警署總部報警。報案人士表示，望警方能嚴正執法，阻止仇恨言語歪風，全力徹查事件，保障香港市民安全。報警者之一的牧師劉先生，質疑言論涉嫌觸犯香港法例第212章《侵害人身罪條例》第5條串謀或唆使謀殺，認為局方必須正視問題嚴重性，避免社會出現暴力事件。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170918/57225734\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170918%2F57225734&d=4ZXabHcFZBev3dktCAp0NPM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=3ba9594f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170918%2F57225734&h=3f99f881\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170918/57225734</a>"},{"pid":"321effe71c00355183aa9a07b7a0c141f397babc","tid":404808,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T11:33:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"83e9557508046ac0e947449712c6756dd21b73be","tid":404808,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T11:35:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5714df34222335bedd21073edb419583e8277ab","t